snippet: For the second straight year Serena Williams saw her bid for a seventh U.S. Open title halted in the semi-finals with a 6-2 7-6(5) loss to Karolina Pliskova on Thursday that also ended her long reign as world number one....
lead_paragraph: For the second straight year Serena Williams saw her bid for a seventh U.S. Open title halted in the semi-finals with a 6-2 7-6(5) loss to Karolina Pliskova on Thursday that also ended her long reign as world number one.

headline.print_headline: Serena Stunned by Pliskova in U.S. Open Semis
headline.main: Serena Stunned by Pliskova in U.S. Open Semis
